title: Square’s IPO Filing Lists Jack Dorsey’s CEO Role At Twitter As A Risk Factor
text: Square filed for its initial public offering today — and buried in the company’s boilerplate risk factors was a big one: CEO Jack Dorsey’s relationship with Twitter.
